settings.second_feature_heading: Become part of the gutsy community

settings.headline: Do you have the guts to change the world?
settings.subheadline: Check out our planet-friendly and ridiculous tasty dog food.

settings.title: planet friendly
settings.content: Gutsy uses insects as an outstanding source of protein. The ecological footprint of insects is 30 times smaller per kg than that of beef. This means that by serving Gutsy you and your dog have the opportunity to reduce your own carbon footprint as well.

settings.title: ridiculously tasty
settings.content: Spoil your dog with crunchy dog food full of flavor. Because your faithful companion only deserves the best.

settings.title: with the experts’ blessing
settings.content: Thanks to our collaboration with accredited experts, we are able to serve fantastic kibble which taste deliciously and digest wonderfully.

settings.title: hypoallergenic
settings.content: Our kibble is hypoallergenic and therefore perfect for dogs with a sensitive stomach. Allergic reactions are a thing of the past, you can ask our loyal customer Otis!

settings.title: high-quality proteins
settings.content: Not all proteins are easy to digest. That is where Gutsy makes the difference. We only use high-quality and easy digestible proteins in our dog food.

settings.title: an ecological alternative
settings.content: Insects do not only have tiny legs, they also have a tiny ecological footprint, you can feed your dog with a clean conscience.

settings.testimonial_content: Quinn is crazy about Gutsy. She has never emptied her bowl so quickly. Best of all, she doesn't even realise that she is doing her part for the climate.
Nono is a proud mother of 4 fantastic puppies. With Gutsy, we have found a perfectly balanced diet for the whole family.
We had to search for a long time for the right food for Henry as he is allergic to all kinds of ingredients, but thanks to Gutsy's hypoallergenic dog food, these allergies are a thing of the past.
